Title: Return to Skyfire
Writer: Daniel J. Goor (created by), Michael Schur (created by), Carly Hallam (story editor), Jessica Polonsky (story editor), Neil Campbell
Actors: Andy Samberg, Stephanie Beatriz, Terry Crews, Melissa Fumero
Plot: When DC Parlov returns to the precinct to report his latest manuscript being stolen, Terry, Jake and Rosa go undercover at a fantasy convention to catch the culprit.
